      "id": "7bf13892_a124240f",
      "file_path": "csit/docker-compose-all.yml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 32,
      "message": "Thanks for adding it to CSIT !\n\nHowever, we cannot be sure that the db schema is fully cerated by db-migrator until we stop the eclipselink ddl generation in pap & api components. Basically editing the below lines in persistence.xml.\n\n<property name=\"javax.persistence.schema-generation.database.action\" value=\"create\" />\n<property name=\"eclipselink.ddl-generation\" value=\"create-or-extend-tables\" />\n<property name=\"eclipselink.ddl-generation.output-mode\" value=\"database\" />\n\nOtherwise, even if few parts are missing, pap & api will attempt to create them while starting. And db-migrator won't have tracking of those actions.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3239,
        "name": "Ram Krishna Verma",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "ramkrishna.verma@gmail.com",
        "username": "ramverma"
      },
      "updated": "2021-08-10 14:02:59.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
